*Ukoliko* odmah ne reagujemo, situacija će biti sve gora. (If we don't react immediately, the situation will get worse.)

Ako *ukoliko* slučajno dođeš kasnije, javite mi se odmah. (If, by any chance, you come later, let me know immediately.)

*Ukoliko* se ne pridržavamo pravila, čeka nas kazna. (If we don't abide by the rules, we will be punished.)

Oni će se zbližiti *ukoliko* se nakon prepirke pomire. (They will become closer if they make up after the quarrel.)